mode.description:
The mode used by the interface:
1 - PIM-SM protocol;
2 - PIM-DM protocol;
3 - PIM-SM and PIM-DM protocol.

pim-silent.description:
Enable or disable PIM silent:
0 - Disable;
1 - Enable.

bfd-state.description:
BFD session state:
0 - INIT;
1 - CREATE;
2 - CONNECT;
3 - UP;
4 - DOWN;
5 - NOT SURPPORT;
6 - ADMIN DOWN;
7 - BFD_ERROR.

join-attr.description:
Join attribute of neighbor:
1 - P;
2 - N/A.

rpset-type.description:
The type of RP set node:
1 - Default;
2 - Static;
3 - BSR;
4 - Embedded.

